headline: 1 Services Stock with Impressive Fundamentals and 2 We Ignore
summary: Business services providers thrive by solving complex operational challenges for their clients, allowing them to focus on their secret sauce. Furthermore, the demand for their offerings is rising as more clients outsource non-core functions, a trend that has enabled the industry to return 18.9% over the past six months, almost identical to the S&P 500.
